Package sailpoint.object

Class CustomGlobal

  • java.lang.Object
    • sailpoint.object.CustomGlobal
  • public class CustomGlobal
extends java.lang.Object
    A class used to maintain a static Map of custom attributes. This can be used as a way to maintain global variables across calls to custom rules.
